    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Genre comprising accounts of travel presented as film, video, or illustrated lectures; usually with narration, intended to give information about and an overall impression of places visited.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
